Why Invest In Baby Baby Cake?

We have seen opportunity within the current hype around rewards tokens, we wanted to create a project which allows users to profit without having to sell, we put our heads together at BabyBabyCake HQ and tried to come up with a way to stop people feeling the need to sell their tokens at a 2x or a 3x. 

We looked at some successful projects and took the best aspects of them and formulated our own contract to allow for investors to profit without dumping, BabyBabyCake is the rewards token that rewards you in one of the biggest rewards tokens in the game right now! 

We’re here to make you millions, not pocket money. 

Get rewarded in BabyCake, get rewarded in Cake. 

Meet The Team

The team comes from a variety of disciplines, some of us are marketers, some are designers and some are software engineers. We have come together to utilise our skills in the highest possible capacity to build a project that allows for EVERYONE to capitalise on the hype around rewards tokens! 

Following the deployment of the contract we are giving you, the community the opportunity to demonstrate just HOW good you are at shilling, sharing and helping us to grow. This project is going to be largely.

We will listen to you, ensure that your voice is heard and give you the opportunity to MULTIPLY your portfolio.

How Does It Work?

The reward system embedded into our smart contract is a complex and highly advanced system; in layman’s terms whenever there is a trade within the Baby Binamon ecosystem, a percentage of that trade is taken to purchase $BMON and redistribute it to our holders based on how much $BabyBinamon they hold.

This is passive income at it’s finest.

Within just one day of launching, our incredible rewards system has redistributed an estimated $100,000 worth of $Binamon, this gem has the potential to change the lives of investors, especially if you think about the potential that $Binamon has to grow from here.

So what are you waiting for? Buy $BabyBinamon and start earning every second of the day, not just whilst you’re at work.

How To Buy $BabyBabyCake

Step 1

Download the MetaMask Chrome Extension or mobile app.

Setup your account & add the Binance Smart Chain to your network list.

Download MetaMask

Step 2

Use Binance / another exchange to purchase BNB and send it over to your MetaMask Wallet Address.

Or if you already have BNB, simply send it to your MetaMask Wallet.

Visit Binance

Step 3

Head over to the PanCake Swap Exchange and swap your BNB for $BABYBABYCAKE.
(if you already hold another token, you can swap that directly for $BABYBABYACKE too)

Buy on Pancake Swap

Step 4

Congratulations! You are now an Official Baby Baby Cake.

Join our Telegram to stay up to date with the teams announcements & progress.

Join Our Telegram

You will need to add BabyBabyCake, BabyCake & Cake to your MetaMask to view all of your rewards.
